The system architecture uses microservices, asynchronous communication, and good design and development practices, ensuring scalability, resilience,.

description: MediConnect is a healthcare management system that facilitates seamless patient-doctor interactions and appointment scheduling. Built with a microservices architecture, it ensures secure access to medical records and efficient management of healthcare services.

name: RealTime-Fraud-Detection
description: The Real-Time Fraud Detection System is designed to detect fraudulent transactions in real-time. Built using a microservice architecture and deployed on AWS, it efficiently handles transaction processing with Kafka, provides real-time notifications with WebSockets, and persists transaction data with PostgreSQL.
